qa_pairs.question: Now, it's my understanding this is a free service at this time, correct?
qa_pairs.answer: Yes, we have a free trial out to all of our customers. We would just need your PCR contract signer to request that AI search or AI candidate match are added to your free trial.

qa_pairs.question: Do you know how long this is going to be free to users?
qa_pairs.answer: The management hasn't really indicated to us how long they want to let the free trial ride. I imagine it'll be for a while because they haven't decided on a date to end it. But we will give everyone a heads up in advance if it's going to be cut off or ending.

qa_pairs.question: And do you have a ballpark as to have you guys discussed what the pricing will be?
qa_pairs.answer: The pricing is part of one of the PCR packages. That kind of changes based on where you are currently in your contract, what you're currently paying. So we could always have our sales rep, Jim Lombardo, reach out to you and discuss your options based on how your current contract is set up.

qa_pairs.question: How long do you think it takes once we set everything in motion?
qa_pairs.answer: It should be turned on within two or three days is what we've seen so far for each account.
